				</div>
			</section>

			<section id="section04">
				<section id="section04-1">
					<div class="inner">
						<strong>안녕하세요</strong> <strong>블룸에 오신것을 환영합니다.</strong>
					</div>
				</section>
				<section id="section04-2">
					<div class="inner">
						<h2>마음 쑥쑥</h2>
						<fieldset>
							<div class="team-member">
								<div class="members">
									<figure>
										<img src="./img/wh.png" alt="">
